# Session state

Status: pending first ontology session.

Start with one question:

What business reality are we modeling first: the whole company, one module, one
production system, one product line, or one new business idea?

Recommended default: start with the smallest boundary that already has real
products, roles, processes, metrics, and decisions.

Capture during the session:

- accepted facts;
- candidate definitions;
- conflicts;
- unknowns;
- source candidates;
- next questions.
